      "message": "[🟡 Suggestions] Line 624: Iterating backgroundDeactivatedAccounts while other executor tasks may add to it can throw ConcurrentModificationException if deactivateProxyAccountsForBackground() is queued again before or during restore processing, or can skip/clear newly recorded accounts. Take a snapshot and remove only restored ids from the set. For example:\n```suggestion\nval accountsToRestore \u003d backgroundDeactivatedAccounts.toList()\nfor (id in accountsToRestore) {\n    val account \u003d mAccountList.firstOrNull { it.accountId \u003d\u003d id }\n    if (account?.isEnabled \u003d\u003d true \u0026\u0026 account.isDhtProxyEnabled) {\n        JamiService.setAccountActive(id, true)\n    }\n    backgroundDeactivatedAccounts.remove(id)\n}\n```",
